  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.messagebox.openlink">開啟下載頁面</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.messagebox.openpackages">套件管理員</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.discord.description">加入我們的伺服器，在 #help 中描述問題。如有需要，請從「說明 → 開啟記錄檔位置」附加記錄檔。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.discord.open">開啟 Discord</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.discord.title">Discord</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.address">lunaiproject@gmail.com</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.copy">複製地址</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.description">若問題難以重現，請寫信給我們並附上記錄檔。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.title">電子郵件</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.write">撰寫郵件</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.message">請告訴我們出了什麼問題。建議優先使用 Discord #help，以便我們盡快回覆；有幫助時請附上記錄檔。也可以透過電子郵件聯絡我們。</system:String>

